# Modul 09 – DEBT
## Abschnitt 27 – Technische Implementierung & Datenarchitektur (V1.1)

---

### Versionslog
- V1.0 – Referenzarchitektur, Datenmodelle, Sicherheitsstandards.
- V1.1 – ASCII-Diagramme, Beispiel-API-Contracts (OpenAPI), Validierungsregeln erweitert, Fehler-/Ratenlimit-Handling, DPIA-Checkliste, Testvektoren.

---

### 1. Ziel und Geltungsbereich
Wie V1.0, erweitert um konkrete Artefakte zur unmittelbaren Implementierung und Prüfung (CCC-ready).

---

### 2. Architekturprinzipien (unverändert, präzisiert)
- Privacy by Design (Datensparsamkeit, Pseudonymisierung, klare Löschkonzepte).
- Offline-first (funktional vollständiger Betrieb ohne Netz).
- Interoperabilität (versionierte Schemas & APIs, OpenAPI 3.1).
- Nachvollziehbarkeit (Signaturen, Prüfsummen, Audit-Trails).
- Resilienz (dezentral, repliziert, konfliktrobuste Syncs).

---

### 3. ASCII-Systemübersicht

```
+-------------------+        TLS 1.3        +-------------------+
|  Client (App/Web) |  <------------------>  |  API Gateway (/v1)|
+---------+---------+                        +----+--------------+
          |                                        |
          | OAuth2/OIDC                            | gRPC/HTTP
          v                                        v
+---------+---------+                        +-----+--------------+
|  Privacy Engine   |                        |  Case Service     |
|  (anon, k-anon)   |                        |  (CRUD Cases)     |
+---------+---------+                        +-----+--------------+
          |                                        |
          v                                        v
+---------+---------+                        +-----+--------------+
|  Ledger Service   |----------------------->|  TRUTH Audit Node |
|  (writeoff, etc.) |   append-only feed     |  (WORM, verify)   |
+-------------------+                        +-------------------+
```

---

### 4. Datenmodelle (Auszug, präzisiert)

#### 4.1 Case (JSON Schema, Draft 2020-12)
```json
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://quest.system/schemas/debt/case/1-1.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["case_id", "created_at", "status", "debt_profile", "privacy_level"],
  "properties": {
    "case_id": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^D-[0-9]{4}-[0-9]{6}$" },
    "created_at": { "type": "string", "format": "date-time" },
    "status": { "enum": ["open","in_review","resolved","archived"] },
    "subject_ref": { "type": "string", "minLength": 6 },
    "debt_profile": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["amount_range","category","currency"],
      "properties": {
        "amount_range": { "enum": ["0-499","500-1999","2000-4999","5000+"] },
        "category": { "enum": ["rent","utilities","medical","education","microcredit","other"] },
        "currency": { "type": "string", "minLength": 3, "maxLength": 3 }
      }
    },
    "actions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["ts","type"],
        "properties": {
          "ts": { "type": "string", "format": "date-time" },
          "type": { "type": "string" },
          "amount": { "type": "number", "minimum": 0 },
          "proof": { "type": "string" },
          "sig": { "type": "string" }
        }
      }
    },
    "privacy_level": { "enum": ["low","medium","high"] },
    "retention_policy": { "type": "string" },
    "truth_link": { "type": "string" }
  }
}
```

#### 4.2 Ledger (nur Änderungen ggü. V1.0)
- Pflichtfeld `op_reason` (enum: grant|policy|negotiation|legal|other)
- `privacy_level` default: `aggregated_public`

---

### 5. Beispiel-API-Contracts (OpenAPI 3.1, Auszug)

```yaml
openapi: 3.1.0
info:
  title: DEBT Core API
  version: 1.1.0
paths:
  /v1/cases:
    post:
      summary: Create case
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/CaseCreate"
      responses:
        "201":
          description: Created
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Case"
        "400":
          description: Validation error
        "401":
          description: Unauthorized
  /v1/ledger:
    post:
      summary: Append anonymised ledger entry
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/LedgerEntryCreate"
      responses:
        "201":
          description: Created
components:
  schemas:
    CaseCreate:
      type: object
      required: [debt_profile, privacy_level]
      properties:
        subject_ref:
          type: string
        debt_profile:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/DebtProfile"
        privacy_level:
          type: string
          enum: [low, medium, high]
    DebtProfile:
      type: object
      required: [amount_range, category, currency]
      properties:
        amount_range: { type: string, enum: ["0-499","500-1999","2000-4999","5000+"] }
        category: { type: string, enum: ["rent","utilities","medical","education","microcredit","other"] }
        currency: { type: string, minLength: 3, maxLength: 3 }
    Case:
      allOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/CaseCreate"
        - type: object
          required: [case_id, created_at, status]
          properties:
            case_id: { type: string }
            created_at: { type: string, format: date-time }
            status: { type: string, enum: ["open","in_review","resolved","archived"] }
    LedgerEntryCreate:
      type: object
      required: [case_id, op, currency]
      properties:
        case_id: { type: string }
        op: { type: string, enum: [grant, buyback, fee_waiver, writeoff] }
        gross: { type: number, minimum: 0 }
        currency: { type: string, minLength: 3, maxLength: 3 }
        op_reason: { type: string, enum: [grant, policy, negotiation, legal, other] }
        proofs: { type: array, items: { type: string } }
```

---

### 6. Fehler- und Ratenlimit-Handling

#### 6.1 Einheitliches Fehlerformat
```json
{
  "error": "validation_error",
  "message": "amount_range missing",
  "correlation_id": "c0a8017e-...",
  "details": [{"path":"/debt_profile/amount_range","rule":"required"}]
}
```

#### 6.2 HTTP-Codes
- 400 Validation, 401 Unauthorized, 403 Forbidden (RBAC), 404 Not Found, 409 Conflict (Sync), 429 Too Many Requests, 500 Server.

#### 6.3 Ratenlimit-Header
- `X-RateLimit-Limit`, `X-RateLimit-Remaining`, `X-RateLimit-Reset`

---

### 7. Datenschutz-Folgenabschätzung (DPIA) – Kurzcheckliste
- Datenkatalog minimiert (keine Klarnamen, ranges statt Beträge).
- Zweckbindung dokumentiert (Entschuldung/Transparenz).
- Aufbewahrungsfristen definiert, Widerrufskanal vorhanden.
- Pseudonymisierung vor jeder Weitergabe.
- Rollen- & Rechtekonzept jährlich geprüft.
- Transfer in Drittländer: nur mit äquivalentem Schutzniveau/offline.

---

### 8. Testvektoren (Beispiele)

#### 8.1 Gültiger CaseCreate
```json
{"debt_profile":{"amount_range":"5000+","category":"rent","currency":"EUR"},"privacy_level":"high"}
```

#### 8.2 Ungültiger CaseCreate
```json
{"debt_profile":{"amount_range":"9999","category":"other","currency":"EU"},"privacy_level":"lowest"}
```

#### 8.3 LedgerEntryCreate valid
```json
{"case_id":"D-2025-000123","op":"writeoff","gross":0,"currency":"EUR","op_reason":"legal","proofs":["sha256:3f..9a"]}
```

---

### 9. Synchronisationsablauf (ASCII-Sequenz)

```
Client       API        CaseSvc       TRUTH
  | POST /cases  |                    |
  |------------->|                    |
  |   201 id     |                    |
  |<-------------|                    |
  | POST /ledger |------------------->| append
  |------------->|                    |
  |   201 rec    |                    |
  |<-------------|          push ---->| verify(hash, sig)
```

---

### 10. Deployment-Profile (konkretisiert)
- Minimal: 1 API (stateless) + 1 Storage (encrypted) + 1 TRUTH Node.
- Standard: 2 API (HA) + 2 Storage (replication) + 1 TRUTH + 1 Privacy Engine.
- Hardenings: HTTPS only, HSTS, CSP, mTLS (service2service), key rotation ≤ 180 Tage.

---

### 11. Rückwärts-/Vorwärtskompatibilität
- Schema „expand-and-contract“, `deprecated`-Felder max. 2 Minor-Releases mitführen.
- API-Versionen parallel betreiben (`/v1`, `/v2`), Migrationsfenster dokumentieren.

---

### 12. Lizenz & Metadaten (verbindlich)
- `licence_id: "QOHL-1.0"` und `licence_url` in jedem exportierten Artefakt.
- Code unter GPLv3, Inhalte unter CC BY-NC-SA 4.0.
- Öffentliche Artefakte: SHA-256 + Ed25519-Signaturen, WORM-Archiv.

---

### 13. Anhang – cURL-Snippets
```bash
# Case anlegen
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" -H "Content-Type: application/json"  -d '{"debt_profile":{"amount_range":"2000-4999","category":"utilities","currency":"EUR"},"privacy_level":"medium"}'  https://api.example.org/v1/cases

# Ledger schreiben
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" -H "Content-Type: application/json"  -d '{"case_id":"D-2025-000123","op":"writeoff","gross":0,"currency":"EUR","op_reason":"legal","proofs":["sha256:..."]}'  https://api.example.org/v1/ledger
```

---

